  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME DESCRIPTION:</h2><br>You receive an email from an ex-girlfriend.<br>From which you will learn that your parting was set up and the girl herself was kidnapped.<br>At the same moment you go in search of your beloved. Ahead of you are waiting for a lot of mysteries and mysticism.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538330/extras/a7bece75440206272510bd821d085df0.poster.avif?t=1707987637\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538330/extras/a7bece75440206272510bd821d085df0.webm?t=1707987637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538330/extras/a7bece75440206272510bd821d085df0.mp4?t=1707987637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is a detective horror thriller with a first-person view, standard controls and a deep storyline.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Two endings.<br></li><li> Open world.<br></li><li> Responsive controls.<br></li><li> Beautiful graphics.<br></li><li> Good optimization.<br></li><li> Tense atmosphere.</li></ul>",
